snippet.textDisplay:
It's been 2 years since we parted ways. It was a beautiful journey of 7 years. But I had to make my decision, it was needed. 
She is now with someone else, happily ever after, they say! 
And here, me and my nights. Not even a single day passed without her remembrance. Now when I hear Kaavish saying, "Jaunga Kahan Main Toh Hoon Yahan, Tere Dil Ki Ahaaton Mein Hoon" I break down. I cry like hell. Kyuki mujhe toh jana nehi tha, nahi use. Magar wo chali gayi aur main tanha reh gaya. Aur shayad hamesha reh jaunga.
